{"tid":1684231,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy Labs已發布，是三星開發的一套和類似Good Lock的系統優化工具","createTime":"2019-10-31T03:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:49:37.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d0cf90a1b3397101c07dbc8283986e89f10fda","tid":1684231,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"@i冰宇宙<br />\nGalaxy Labs已發布，是三星開發的一套和類似Good Lock的系統優化工具。<br />\nGood Lock是系統美化工具箱<br />\nGalaxy Labs是系統優化工具箱。<br />\n這裏邊目前有四個組件：<br />\n電池衛士 Battery Guardian  自動優化、睡眠應用程序<br />\n電池跟蹤器 Battery Tracker  跟蹤app耗電量和時間<br />\n文件衛士 File Guardian  可以恢覆手機已刪除的文件<br />\n應用助推器 App Booster 提升App性能達15%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JK2F9Lw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJK2F9Lw.jpg&h=504e0de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu2F9Lw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu2F9Lw.jpg&h=cee36be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i97iWqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi97iWqz.jpg&h=3d7193bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHNOzcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHNOzcf.jpg&h=b7d2093d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQQP25B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQQP25B.jpg&h=d4caa68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uH5HDDX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuH5HDDX.jpg&h=ae118f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9nfech.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9nfech.jpg&h=2448d45a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySXZFSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySXZFSi.jpg&h=127ebbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"h